raceComments: {"comment":"The final ever Cox Plate is to be run on this circuit until the new track is set down in a couple of years. What a race it has been, and this year's version is another cracker, with defending champ 6. VIA SISTINA is all set to win again after a solid effort for third in the G1 Turnbull Stakes, when settling too far off the leaders on a slow speed. JMac has been down on his best lately and will need this to get some confidence back. 2. ANTINO has been building his form nicely this season and looks to be peaking at the right time. He has been placed in both of his starts here and will give his rivals plenty to think about. 8. AELIANA was another to run on too late in the Turnbull Stakes, finishing fifth. She was runner-up in both of her starts before that, and will have Hugh Bowman in the saddle this time. With the right trip, she can have the last say. 7. TREASURETHE MOMENT tried hard at Caulfield 2 weeks ago but lacked her usual finishing sprint. She will be spot-on for this.","runners":[6,2,8,7],"exclusive":true}
